#text=I wanted to go the museum downtown Milwaukee .
#text=I got ten dollars from my bank and put in my pocket .
#text=I walked a block from my house to catch the bus .
#text=The number nine bus came ten minutes later .
#text=I boarded the bus and asked the driver “ How much ? ”
#text=The driver asked me where I was going and when I told him he said “ That� ll be two seventy five . ”
#text=I pulled three dollars out of my pocket and put them in the bus money collection machine .
#text=The machine showed three dollars were entered and that my ride would cost two seventy five .
#text=A quarter dropped in the drop box .
#text=I retrieved the quarter and then found a seat .
#text=The bus driver told I had ten stops before mine so I started counting stops .
#text=I pulled the bus s rider cord to let the bus driver I wanted to get off .
#text=The bus let me off in the front of the Milwaukee Public Museum .
#text=I spent almost the whole day there and then returned home the opposite way I came .
